No matter the results, I will always be proud of you, because your worth is so much greater than any exam. Still, I truly believe that your efforts will be rewarded and that you will look back on tomorrow with a smile. Rest well tonight, believe in yourself, and remember how deeply you are loved and supported. Wishing you all the luck and success in the world, my darling. You've got this, and I cannot wait to celebrate with you afterward.

